---
description: Tauri v2 IPC and store conventions
alwaysApply: true
---

Every new #[command] requires allow-[command-name] in src-tauri/capabilities/default.json. Tauri v2 Channel uses .onmessage NOT .onData(). camelCase JS keys auto-convert to snake_case Rust args — never manually convert. Use handle.store() via StoreExt, never handle.get_store().
